  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p>Install BarcodeScanner-4.5.1.apk from the downloads section on a Kindle Fire HDX<br>
Notice that the UI is properly oriented in landscape mode but the camera preview is inverted (up-side-down)</p>

<p>The UI should be properly oriented in landscape mode (as it is) but the camera preview should also be right-side-up.</p>

<p>This issue occurs whether the Kindle's "Auto-Rotate" feature is enabled or disabled.</p>

<p><a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a54c8c77e06161b480be4b6adfb70162a8c50fcd/68747470733a2f2f662e636c6f75642e6769746875622e636f6d2f6173736574732f3832323532322f313934373235392f64336363626565342d383034372d313165332d383137612d3865333362356236313436622e706e67" target="_blank"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/a54c8c77e06161b480be4b6adfb70162a8c50fcd/68747470733a2f2f662e636c6f75642e6769746875622e636f6d2f6173736574732f3832323532322f313934373235392f64336363626565342d383034372d313165332d383137612d3865333362356236313436622e706e67" alt="device-2014-01-15-101638" data-canonical-src="https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/822522/1947259/d3ccbee4-8047-11e3-817a-8e33b5b6146b.png" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>

<p>Ported from <a href="https://code.google.com/p/zxing/issues/detail?id=1833">https://code.google.com/p/zxing/issues/detail?id=1833</a></p>
