  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p>I can reproduce this with the Samsung Galaxy Tab 2 7.0.</p>

<p>Steps to reproduce:<br>
1. Enable screen rotation<br>
2. Flip to the right<br>
3. Disable screen rotation<br>
4. Open Barcode Scanner<br>
5. See screenshot</p>

<p>If bryancal is not reachable anymore I can test with BS+ if you want.</p>

<p>Another interesting behavior is that when you do not disable the screen rotation (step 3) the screen is flipped by 180 degrees:<br>
<a href="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/76147cd00662f7028b53e2f698e82083cf2748c4/68747470733a2f2f662e636c6f75642e6769746875622e636f6d2f6173736574732f3139353336372f323236373932382f37666630616666652d396563312d313165332d386161662d3937653734666338346262642e706e67" target="_blank"><img src="https://camo.githubusercontent.com/76147cd00662f7028b53e2f698e82083cf2748c4/68747470733a2f2f662e636c6f75642e6769746875622e636f6d2f6173736574732f3139353336372f323236373932382f37666630616666652d396563312d313165332d386161662d3937653734666338346262642e706e67" alt="device-2014-02-26-093908" data-canonical-src="https://f.cloud.github.com/assets/195367/2267928/7ff0affe-9ec1-11e3-8aaf-97e74fc84bbd.png" style="max-width:100%;"></a></p>
