  <div class="comment-content">

    <div class="edit-comment-hide">
      <div class="comment-body markdown-body email-format js-comment-body">
          <div class="email-fragment">Not sure what to make of that. The app does not set any camera rotation
params and never has:

<a href="https://github.com/zxing/zxing/blob/master/android/src/com/google/zxing/client/android/camera/CameraConfigurationManager.java">https://github.com/zxing/zxing/blob/master/android/src/com/google/zxing/client/android/camera/CameraConfigurationManager.java</a>

The only way a working device would do this is if the wrong rotation params
were set, so this looks like a device problem.

Weirdly it may be caused by a different problem with a different camera
param. Try all the workarounds in settings.</div>
